40|$|In {{these studies}} the isotopic {{inventories}} and corresponding activities of important nuclides for different <b>fuel</b> <b>cycles</b> of a CANDU reactor have been compared. The calculations {{have been performed}} using the computer code WIMSD 4. The isotopic inventories and activities have been calculated versus the fuel burn-up for the natural UO 2 fuel, 1. 2 % enriched UO 2 fuel and for the 0. 45 % PuO 2 -UO 2 fuel. It is found that 1. 2 % enriched uranium fuel has the lowest activity as compared to other two <b>fuel</b> <b>cycles</b> and vice versa for the 0. 45 % PuO 2 -UO 2 fuel...|$|R
