40|$|This chapter {{looks at}} Generation IV nuclear reactors, {{such as the}} very {{high-temperature}} reactor (VHTR), the supercritical water reactor (SCWR), the molten salt reactor (MSR), the sodium-cooled fast reactor (SFR), the lead-cooled fast reactor (LFR) and the gas-cooled fast reactor (GFR). Reactor designs and <b>fuel</b> <b>cycles</b> are also described...|$|R
